negotiator.parties

Class AbstractNegotiationParty

  • java.lang.Object
    • negotiator.parties.AbstractNegotiationParty
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, NegotiationParty
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BoaParty

    public abstract class AbstractNegotiationParty
extends java.lang.Object
implements NegotiationParty
    A basic implementation of the NegotiationParty interface. This basic implementation sets up some common variables for you.
    Author:
    David Festen, Reyhan (The random bid generator)
